LocalDeviceBuildProvider

public class LocalDeviceBuildProvider
extends StubBuildProvider

java.lang.Object
   ↳ com.android.tradefed.build.StubBuildProvider
     ↳ com.android.tradefed.build.LocalDeviceBuildProvider

A IBuildProvider that constructs a IDeviceBuildInfo based on a provided filesystem directory path.

Specific device build files are recognized based on a configurable set of patterns.
